{"id":292936,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/global-voices-中国梦是强军梦吗？/","date":"2013-05-10T14:30:16Z","modified":"2013-05-10T14:30:16Z","title":"Global Voices | 中国梦是强军梦吗？","content":"<p><p>3月3日<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.chinamil.com.cn/jfjbmap/content/2013-03/03/content_29058.htm\">解放军日报</a>在头版登了“聚焦建立‘强军’梦”一文。乍看之下，这似乎是出现在两会，由人大会议发布的典型宣传。“强军梦关键在于听命政党”、“勤奋效率工作是成功的基石”等口号不断重复，充斥全文。更深看来，也许更像是一种政治呼应，预告国家预算揭幕日（星期二）预算将有提升。中国预计在2013年，将720.2亿元人民币（相当于114.3亿美元）用于军事，<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887324178904578339243545311174.html?mod=djemITPA_t\">较</a>去年增长10.7％。</p>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/tea-leaf-nation/\" title=\"文章导读 Tea Leaf Nation\">Tea Leaf Nation</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/portnoy/\" title=\"文章导读 Portnoy\">Portnoy</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/03/11/is-the-china-dream-really-a-strong-military-dream/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/05/10/12475/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%A2%A6%E6%98%AF%E5%BC%BA%E5%86%9B%E6%A2%A6%E5%90%97%EF%BC%9F&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F05%2F10%2F12475%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F05%2F10%2F12475%2F&#038;desc=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%A2%A6%E6%98%AF%E5%BC%BA%E5%86%9B%E6%A2%A6%E5%90%97%EF%BC%9F\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>